cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper discusses the design of wireless networks that utilize spectrum and energy harvesting techniques to improve efficiency and availability. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of renewable energy, which falls under cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper's focus on optimization and control also suggests it could fall under cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper mentions emergency communication capacity, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
